{
  "texts": [
    "The relative question influence increases with more challenging datasets.",
    "In order to further explore this observation, Figure 10 determines whether the question influence is directly linked to the complexity of a question.",
    "The data complexity classifier (QC system) is used to rank all the contexts according to their complexity.",
    "Then retaining a certain fraction of the most complex contexts, the relative question influence is plotted.",
    "The curve is plotted for all the datasets combined and RACE++ on its own."
  ]
}